Texts.Chs:
驾驭能量的的太空猫咪，失踪多年。
如果他们重新露面，请告诉富兰克林宇宙号的全体船员，因为我们需要从头开始重做他们。

^orange;［天赋］^reset;
增益：移动速度^green;+10%^reset;，跳跃高度^green;+10%^reset;
抗性：寒冷抗性^green;+20%^reset;，毒素抗性^green;+20%^reset;
夜间时：^green;暗影力量会回复你的生命值^reset;

^orange;［武器］^reset;
魔杖，法杖：伤害^green;+25%^reset;，^green;增加^reset;能量回复速度
长棍：伤害^green;+15%^reset;，防御^green;+3^reset;

^red;［弱点］^reset;
减益：能量值上限^red;-5%^reset;
抗性：暗影抗性^red;-25%^reset;，电系抗性^red;-15%^reset;

Texts.Eng:
Energy-wielding space cats. Missing for years. If they reappear again, please tell the FU crew since we'll need to redo them from scratch.

  -^red;5% Energy, 25% Weakness: Shadow, 15% Weakness: Electric^reset;
  +^green;10% Speed, +10% Jump, +20% Ice Resist, +20% Poison Resist^reset;
  ^green;During the night, shadowy power restores your health^reset;
  Wand/Staff: +^green;25% Damage. Also gain Energy regeneration increase^reset;
  Quarterstaff: +^green;15% Damage , +3 Protection^reset;
